abstract: Roger Federer announces that he will skip the 2015 Davis Cup; other tennis news noted.
lead_paragraph: Roger Federer, who won his first-round match in Dubai on Monday, will skip the Davis Cup this year, having led Switzerland in 2014 to its first title.

headline.main: Federer Won’t Play in the Davis Cup
headline.print_headline: Federer Won’t Play in the Davis Cup
